---
const pageTitle = "vtur | Sistema de Gerenciamento de Vendas";
const description = "Site institucional do vtur para produto, planos, precos e demonstracao comercial.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b0f2a" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.webmanifest" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #fbfbfd;
        --ink: #0b0f2a;
        --ink-soft: #475569;
        --line: rgba(11, 15, 42, 0.08);
        --accent: #7c3aed;
        --accent-soft: #a855f7;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Manrope, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.16), transparent 34%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.16), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f7ff 100%);
      }

      .shell {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      header {
        padding: 28px 0 12px;
      }

      .brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }

      .brand img {
        width: 54px;
        height: 54px;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }

      .brand strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .brand span {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
      }

      .hero {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(280px, 0.9fr);
        gap: 28px;
        padding: 28px 0 72px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 18px 0 14px;
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      }

      p.lead {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 52ch;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 48px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .btn.primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-soft));
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.18);
      }

      .btn.secondary {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--ink);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      }

      .panel {
        background: var(--panel);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 22px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(11, 15, 42, 0.08);
      }

      .panel img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .mini-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 18px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
      }

      .mini-card strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .mini-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 0 0 48px;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          padding-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="shell">
      <header>
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <img src="/brand/vtur-symbol.png" alt="Simbolo do vtur" />
          <div>
            <strong>vtur</strong>
            <span>Sistema de Gerenciamento de Vendas</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </header>

      <main class="hero">
        <section>
          <span class="eyebrow">Repositorio institucional</span>
          <h1>vtur para vendas, operacao e crescimento comercial.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Esta base separa o marketing do produto da aplicacao operacional. Aqui ficam homepage,
            planos, precos, provas de valor, SEO e paginas de conversao do dominio `vtur.com.br`.
          </p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="https://vtur.app">Abrir app</a>
            <a class="btn secondary" href="#proximos-passos">Ver roadmap inicial</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <aside class="panel">
          <img src="/brand/vtur-logo-horizontal.svg" alt="Logo do vtur" />
          <div class="grid" id="proximos-passos">
            <article class="mini-card">
              <strong>Produto</strong>
              <p>Explicar modulos, rotina comercial, indicadores e operacao em uma narrativa clara.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="mini-card">
              <strong>Comercial</strong>
              <p>Publicar planos, precos, CTA para demo e captura de leads qualificados.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="mini-card">
              <strong>SEO</strong>
              <p>Estruturar conteudo evergreen para busca organica e posicionamento do vtur no mercado.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </main>

      <footer>
        Base inicial pronta para evolucao do site institucional em `vtur.com.br`.
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
